  => src/.arch-ids/b.id	test/.arch-ids/b.id
  * update pristine tree (tla@mercurial--convert/tla--test--0--patch-4 => tla--test--0--patch-5)
  * committed tla@mercurial--convert/tla--test--0--patch-5
  $ cd ..

